    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 197030,
      "reputation" : 1696,
      "user_id" : 440827,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 86,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6e828328eaca6c55497944f10f3f71cf?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Christian",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/440827/christian"
    },
    "is_accepted" : true,
    "score" : 6,
    "last_activity_date" : 1461931057,
    "creation_date" : 1461931057,
    "answer_id" : 36937796,
    "question_id" : 36912500,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>if you check the <a href=\"https://github.com/ChristianLutz/keycloak/blob/1.9.x/adapters/oidc/servlet-filter/src/main/java/org/keycloak/adapters/servlet/KeycloakOIDCFilter.java\" rel=\"noreferrer\">KeycloakOIDCFilter</a> you see there are three additional parameter.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>keycloak.config.resolver</li>\n<li>keycloak.config.file</li>\n<li>keycloak.config.path</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We are using file parameter and works like charme.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 14983151,
      "reputation" : 750,
      "user_id" : 10816587,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/qLZ1Y.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "MichaelCkr",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/10816587/michaelckr"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 3,
    "last_activity_date" : 1763022104,
    "last_edit_date" : 1763022104,
    "creation_date" : 1545322490,
    "answer_id" : 53872319,
    "question_id" : 36912500,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The Servlet-Filter mentioned above is not necessary.</p>\n<p>It is enough to set a context-parameter, like @OkieOth said in his comment.</p>\n<p>E.g. set a Parameter like this</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;Parameter name=&quot;keycloak.config.file&quot; value=&quot;MY-PATH/keycloak.json&quot; override=&quot;false&quot;/&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>within your context (beside the for keycloak configured Valve) or a &quot;context-param&quot; in your web application deployment descriptor (/WEB-INF/web.xml):</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;context-param&gt;\n    &lt;param-name&gt;keycloak.config.file&lt;/param-name&gt;\n    &lt;param-value&gt;MY-PATH/keycloak.json&lt;/param-value&gt;\n&lt;/context-param&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>For more Detail about context-params, see <a href=\"https://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-5.5-doc/config/context.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">The Context Container</a> in section &quot;Context Parameters&quot;.</p>\n"
  } ],
